-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Installing Redux

---> npm install --save redux

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Three Principles of Redux

1) Single source of truth
2) State is read-only
3) Changes are made with pure functions

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Installing React-Redux

---> npm install --save react-redux

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Redux Concepts :

1) Actions
2) Action Creators
3) Reducers
4) Store

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
